fibonacci-series_key3: Iss series ka `pehla_number 0` hai aur `dusra_number` 1 hai. Aur uske baad har number `peechle do` numbers ka `sum` hota hai
fibonacci-series_key5: Aap isse recursion ka use kar kar - ek function banaye `fib` jo `number` parameter lekar uske corresponding `fibonacci number` return karta ho.
fibonacci-series_key7: Yeh ek aisi recursion hai jismei current value - ussi function ki last do values par depend karta hai.
fibonacci-series_key10: Aap apni understanding expand karne ke liye yeh video dekh sakte hai.
